text:
Park Avenue, north from 55th Street, showing the Ritz Tower apartments on N. E. corner of 57th Street.
The South Kensington (No. 441) apartments on the N. E. corner of 56th Street, as well as the small building, on the S. E. corner, are old, dating back to the 1880's. 1932.
Ewing Galloway, Photographer.
